Citroën (French pronunciation: [si.tʁɔ.ɛn]) is a French automobile manufacturer founded in 1919 by the French industrialist André-Gustave Citroën, and part of the PSA Peugeot Citroën group since 1976.
In 1934, the firm established its reputation for innovative technology with the Traction Avant.[4] This car was the world's first mass-produced front wheel drive car, and also one of the first to feature a unitary type body, with no chassis supporting the mechanical components.[5]

descriptionHtml:
Welcome to Citroen Wallpapers, the ultimate app for every Citroen enthusiast! Dive into a world where the elegance of French cars meets the convenience of technology. Our app offers an extensive collection of Citroen Car Wallpapers that cater to every taste, ensuring that your device stands out with style and sophistication.

Key Features:

- Easy to Use: Navigate our user-friendly interface to find your favorite Citroen wallpapers effortlessly.
- Favorites: Save your beloved Citroen images for quick access, making it easier to customize your device anytime.
- Set as Wallpaper and Lock Screen: Personalize your smartphone or tablet with stunning Citroen backgrounds as your wallpaper or lockscreen.
- Share with Friends: Spread the love for Citroen by sharing cool car wallpapers with your friends directly from the app.
- Compatibility: Designed for both smartphones and tablets, ensuring a seamless experience across all your devices.
- Dark Mode: Enjoy browsing Citroen Wallpapers in dark mode, reducing eye strain during nighttime use.

Featured Citroen Models:
Our app showcases a wide range of Citroen models, from the sleek modern cars to the powerful muscle cars, and the timeless classics. Revel in the beauty of models such as the Citroen DS, C3, C4 Picasso, and the muscle prowess of the Citroen GT. For those who admire the charm of classic car wallpapers, our collection includes the legendary Citroen 2CV and the Citroen SM. Each wallpaper highlights the unique attributes of these iconic models, making them perfect Citroen backgrounds for your device.

Immerse yourself in a collection rich with Citroen Car Wallpapers, cool car wallpapers, and Citroen lockscreen images. Whether you're a fan of modern car designs, muscle car robustness, or the exquisite craftsmanship of French cars, our app is your gateway to the best Citroen Wallpapers and classic car wallpapers. Discover an array of Citroen images that celebrate the legacy and innovation of Citroen backgrounds.

Disclaimer:

All images used in this app are believed to be in the public domain. If you own rights to any of the images or trademark rights and do not want them to appear here, please contact us at bokyungfasriosu@gmail.com. The content will be deleted immediately. Thanks.

Enhance your device with the elegance of Citroen. Download Citroen Wallpapers now and let your screen showcase the beauty of French automotive artistry.
